  "texts": [
    "All extracts were combined, filtered, precipitated, and then condensed to one-tenth of the original volume using a rotary evaporator.",
    "The resultant suspension was packaged, sealed, and autoclaved.",
    "The main compounds in the Salia miltiorrhiza extracts, tanshinones and salvianolic acids, were determined by TLC, UPLC and HPLC.",
    "The standards tanshinone I (TI) tanshinone IIA (TIIA), dihydrotanshinone I (DI) and cryptotanshinone (CT) were used for analysis of the tanshinones, while salvianolic acid A (SAA) and salvianolic acid B (SAB) were used as the standards for salvianolic acids.",
    "TLC analysis was performed with GF254 silica gel plate."
  ],
